ON SELECTION BAR 1 OF tablas do form frmaparatos01
ON SELECTION BAR 2 OF tablas do form frmaparatos03
ON SELECTION BAR 3 OF tablas do form frmpase05

DEFINE POPUP pasedeguar MARGIN RELATIVE SHADOW COLOR SCHEME 4
DEFINE BAR 1 OF pasedeguar PROMPT "Control de Pase"
ON SELECTION BAR 1 OF pasedeguar do form frmpase01

DEFINE POPUP listados MARGIN RELATIVE SHADOW COLOR SCHEME 4
DEFINE BAR 1 OF listados PROMPT "Averia en consultorios"
ON SELECTION BAR 1 OF listados do form frmpase08


